Merck KGaA Plans to Cut Jobs at Unit in Switzerland, FTD Says

-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 
2011-04-10T16:20:16Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-10/merck-kgaa-plans-to-cut-jobs-at-unit-in-switzerland-ftd-says.html
Merck KGaA (MRK)  wants to cut jobs,
mainly at its Merck Serono unit in  Switzerland , to lower
expenses,  Financial Times Deutschland  reported, citing
unidentified people with knowledge of the plans.  Merck Serono employs about 17,000 people, the newspaper
said in an e-mailed preview of a story that will run tomorrow.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
 nmagnusson1@bloomberg.net ;  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at   acullen8@bloomberg.net  